Why choose ÖresundsTaxi?

With over 20 years of experience, we are Malmö's most trusted taxi company. Here's what makes us unique.

24/7 Service

We are here for you 24/7, every day of the year. No matter the time or weather, you can count on our service.

Local Drivers

Our experienced drivers know Malmö like the back of their hand and always give you the best route to your destination.

Competitive Prices

Transparent prices with no hidden fees. You always know how much your trip will cost before you get in the taxi.
